name: DRIVE TO SPACE
description:
Drive To Space is collaboration project between me as an Animator with an amazing Music Producer / Synthwave Artist from Liverpool, Uk. The one and only, KALAX (@iamkalax).

Drive To Space is about our journey, this is the reflection about how we love about synthwave music, 80's aesthetic and cyberpunk. hope you can feel this vibe.

1920 x 1080 px | 36 second loop animation video
3d Animation by Racun Visual Studio | Music by Kalax | 2021
